Diagram 2 (Cutting on the right)
[{\rtf1\fbidis\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\ltrpar\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par What if black cuts on the right side with 1?
\par
\par White will capture the stone with 2. Continuing, if black plays at 3, white will play 4.
\par
\par It will become clear in the next diagram whether this sequence is right or wrong.
\par }
