Diagram 4 (Black, Takes Profit)
[{\rtf1\fbidis\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\ltrpar\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par In response to blacks cut, if white captures the cutting stone with 1, black captures white's stones in the corner with 2 and 4, making a large profit.
\par
\par This result is satisfactory to black.
\par
\par The pattern variants after Diagram 3 will be dealt with in the next basic diagram.
\par }
